com.apple.audio.toolbox
Class MusicTrack

java.lang.Object
  com.apple.audio.CAObject
      com.apple.audio.toolbox.MusicTrack
public final class MusicTrack
extends CAObject

A Music track is attached from an MusicSequence and contains events that are ordered by their time values.

    MusicTrack properties are:
  • AUNode (in the AUGraph) of the AudioUnit addressed by the MusicTrack
  • textual info
  • mute / solo state
  • offset time
  • loop time and number of loops
  • time units for the event timestamps (beats, seconds, ...) beats go through tempo map, seconds map absolute time
For the track editing operations, all time ranges are as follows [starttime, endtime]. In other words, the range includes the start time, but includes events only up to, but NOT including the end time...
